platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: 自煮健身餐 美味又經濟

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Working out regularly is great, but good health truly begins in the kitchen. This visually dazzling app offers dozens of meal ideas in clever categories like low-carb lunches and post-exercise snacks. Brilliant photos and simple instructions make these recipes easy to follow even for novice chefs, and the built-in shopping list groups items together by grocery-store aisle for shopping efficiency. Now all we need is an app that forces us to hit the gym.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: Skip the takeout and eat healthy at home.
